    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124540/extras/6f08304a3b49ba7017ba87dffd9c7bdd.poster.avif?t=1771932375\" width=616 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124540/extras/6f08304a3b49ba7017ba87dffd9c7bdd.webm?t=1771932375\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124540/extras/6f08304a3b49ba7017ba87dffd9c7bdd.mp4?t=1771932375\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>长枪快马，披挂出发！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >组成一支机器牛仔赏金猎手团，从小镇治安官那里接受危险合约。与好友一起，在4人合作模式中追踪穷凶极恶的目标，将其击败，并领取赏金。这可不是什么轻松差事，不过总得有人干！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124540/extras/6131dbc885246e2864a8637d72170eb1.poster.avif?t=1771932375\" width=616 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124540/extras/6131dbc885246e2864a8637d72170eb1.webm?t=1771932375\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124540/extras/6131dbc885246e2864a8637d72170eb1.mp4?t=1771932375\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>狂野西部，野上加野</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这里可不是你熟悉的狂野西部。除了尘土飞扬的酒馆和一望无际的沙漠，这里还有闹鬼的矿井、复生的骷髅以及无处不在的致命风暴。在这里，你将完成凶险的合约任务，探索诅咒之地，还要时刻小心那巨大无比的幽灵列车。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124540/extras/983fe5cf51c895eae1b74daadbccc4c2.poster.avif?t=1771932375\" width=616 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124540/extras/983fe5cf51c895eae1b74daadbccc4c2.webm?t=1771932375\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124540/extras/983fe5cf51c895eae1b74daadbccc4c2.mp4?t=1771932375\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>快拔枪，快施法，一起活</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在面对一波波敌人和强大的首领时，你和队友可以在左轮手枪和火球术之间无缝切换，个性化自身装备，还可以组合你们的法术。你们必须团队协作、临场应变，才能不断深入未知区域，解锁更困难的挑战和更高级的奖励。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124540/extras/59a827606ed5b6724e582f30475818a2.poster.avif?t=1771932375\" width=616 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124540/extras/59a827606ed5b6724e582f30475818a2.webm?t=1771932375\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124540/extras/59a827606ed5b6724e582f30475818a2.mp4?t=1771932375\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>个性选择，强力升级</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以在小镇进行交易，为你的枪支、法术和技能进行升级。挑选合适的特长，打造强大无比的赏金猎手。你可以选择伤害、治疗或爆头专精，并解锁皮肤来个性化你的机器牛仔和胯下坐骑，让你的《遥遥西土》之旅变得风骚无比。</p>",
